item.title: CVE-2022-35241|2024-08-03T09:29:17.434Z -- f5 -- nginx%20instance%20manager
item.description: In versions 2.x before 2.3.1 and all versions of 1.x, when NGINX Instance Manager is in use, undisclosed requests can cause an increase in disk resource utilization. Note: Software versions which have reached End of Technical Support (EoTS) are not evaluated.
